des: Southeast Texas' newest radio station. Playing the "Greatest Hits of All Time", and the best of the music from the area. We're "Breaking All The Rules". Southeast Texas is known for its musical influences. You'll hear it all here! Gary Lee Love, John L, Dana Melancon, Paul Chargois, Krissy Melancon, Tod Treme. Great local personalities. Listen to The Southeast Texas Express. It's the only station you'll ever need.
